    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors appropriately scoped out at MRL 2. CFD predictions of relative hemolysis index agree with FDA benchmark experimental data within 3.2% across all five nominal operating points. Worst-case hemolysis condition identified at 4 L/min, 4000 RPM with RH = 1.02, meeting the RH < 1 acceptance criterion relative to predicate device. The credibility evidence is sufficient to support the regulatory submission decision for this Class II CPB device.",
